                     <interp inst="t17780916-65-verdict343" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder40s"></interp>
               GUILTY of stealing to the value of 39 s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Tried by the Second Middlesex Jury before Mr. COMMON SERJEANT.</p>
